{"tid":2481641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗阿布泰 仲有好多黃色網店：好生活、同人辦館、 瓹窿瓹罅、蟹貨倉、黃色港口、煲底市集、光時⋯⋯","createTime":"2021-04-09T11:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T03:48:05.000Z","uid":48083,"like":132,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"a8e3dde10da29ee69dbbd94486ce24e00d4c7502","tid":2481641,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T11:50:40.000Z","msg":"好生活：<br />\n<a href=\"https://goodlife.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoodlife.com.hk%2F&d=ke1AtGtnimFyOKizm7Qk%2BWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=91ab961a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goodlife.com.hk/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/goodlifecomhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fgoodlifecomhk%2F&d=ke1AtGtnimFyOKizm7Qk%2BWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=bb91d178\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/goodlifecomhk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>1. 同人辦館 <a href=\"https://ourhkmall.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fourhkmall.com%2F&d=ke1AtGtnimFyOKizm7Qk%2BWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=0ffe96cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ourhkmall.com/</a> </strong></ins><br />\n免運費門檻: 買滿 $500<br />\n送貨時間: 2-4 星期<br />\n貨品分類: 口罩、糧油雜貨、家居用品、護理保健、護膚化妝、母嬰用品、文具書本<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\">&gt; 咁多間入面個網頁做得最靚，介面搜尋等都好易用，最鍾意佢碌落去就有得睇貨，唔洗不斷按下一頁</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n &gt; 零食選擇有大路野之餘都有啲細 brand<br />\n &gt; 有香港品牌 section ，好似辣殺、Year 28、少爺麥啤咁<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>2. 瓹窿瓹罅 <a href=\"https://www.guruguruhk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guruguruhk.com%2F&d=ke1AtGtnimFyOKizm7Qk%2BWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=3e7cc131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.guruguruhk.com/</a></ins></strong><br />\n免運費門檻: 買滿 $300（買滿 $450 有上門環保回收服務）<br />\n送貨時間: 無特別寫明<br />\n貨品分類: 零食、飲品、美容潔膚、寵物、嬰兒、環保<br />\n<span class=\"teal\"> &gt; 免運費門檻咁多間最低，買兩包「光城香米」已夠數</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n &gt; 有本地貨 section <br />\n &gt; 盛惠 $98 既2020愛情運勢網上推算 + 流年網上運程<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>3. 蟹貨倉 <a href=\"https://www.crabwarehouse.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crabwarehouse.com%2F&d=ke1AtGtnimFyOKizm7Qk%2BWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=bec3f9a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.crabwarehouse.com/</a></ins></strong><br />\n免運費門檻: 買滿 $300 （健身用品除外，要買滿 $550 先送）<br />\n送貨時間: 2-3 星期<br />\n貨品分類: 口罩、健身用品、瑜伽用品、家居清潔、黃色產物、<br />\n<br />\n &gt; 主打強身健體貨品<br />\n &gt; 防具同口罩選擇呢間最齊<br />\n &gt; 啞鈴、阻力帶、甚至健身椅都有<br />\n<span class=\"teal\"> &gt; 愛國用品及 TEE 令人驚喜，大推！</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>4. HMarket <a href=\"https://www.hmarket.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hmarket.com.hk%2F&d=ke1AtGtnimFyOKizm7Qk%2BWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=49711a60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hmarket.com.hk/</a></ins></strong><br />\n免運費門檻: 買滿 $500<br />\n送貨時間: 1-2 星期<br />\n貨品分類: 口罩、零食、飲品、美容、環保<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\"> &gt; 口罩選擇多，豬咀同濾器都有</span><br />\n &gt; 零食同野飲有唔少係英國貨<br />\n<br />\n5. 台灣代購：<br />\nSupport_twbro <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/supporttwbro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsupporttwbro&d=ke1AtGtnimFyOKizm7Qk%2BWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=333c7e94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/supporttwbro</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://Yellowbirds.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FYellowbirds.hk&d=ke1AtGtnimFyOKizm7Qk%2BWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=90630a45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://Yellowbirds.hk</a> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yellowbirds.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyellowbirds.hk%2F&d=ke1AtGtnimFyOKizm7Qk%2BWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=e49676f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yellowbirds.hk/</a><br />\n台灣維城士多 (即將開幕) <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/victoriastoreTW/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FvictoriastoreTW%2F&d=ke1AtGtnimFyOKizm7Qk%2BWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=b2e0fca7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/victoriastoreTW/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>7.光時 <a href=\"https://www.hkongs.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkongs.com%2F&d=ke1AtGtnimFyOKizm7Qk%2BWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=e4af560a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkongs.com/</a></ins></strong><br />\n免運費門檻: 買滿 $500<br />\n送貨時間: 2-3 星期<br />\n貨品分類: 零食、飲品、家品、護理、寵物、藥物健康<br />\n<br />\n &gt; 最老字號既黃店網購，但貨品選擇唔算好多<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>9. 黃色港口 <a href=\"https://www.yellowporthk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yellowporthk.com%2F&d=ke1AtGtnimFyOKizm7Qk%2BWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=a69628e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.yellowporthk.com/</a></ins></strong><br />\n免運費門檻: 搵唔到邊到有寫...<br />\n送貨時間: 無特別寫明<br />\n貨品分類: 零食、醬料、手工啤、文創、時裝、寵物用品、護膚品<br />\n<br />\n &gt; 有本地貨 section <br />\n &gt; 手作精品選擇比較多<br />\n<strong><ins><br />\n10. 煲底市集 <a href=\"https://www.stand-with-hk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stand-with-hk.com%2F&d=ke1AtGtnimFyOKizm7Qk%2BWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=7434cec7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.stand-with-hk.com/</a></ins></strong><br />\n免運費門檻: $350<br />\n送貨時間: 無特別寫明<br />\n貨品分類: 口罩、零食、醬料、寵物用品、廚具<br />\n<br />\n &gt; 有賣黃色手作精品"},{"pid":"d0069179d08a2a83f241a507a56972336ba56a36","tid":2481641,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T11:51:21.000Z","msg":"原post<br />\n<br />\n【唔想幫襯血汗工廠?】10 大網購黃店總彙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2130876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2130876</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ecdfbc03ba2dca32c08d8b42f210577831d32f85","tid